    skos:prefLabel "Chemical Warfare Agents"@en ;
    skos:definition "Chemical agents or ‘chemical warfare agents’ (chemical weapons) are chemicals, including dual -use chemicals, used to cause intentional death or harm through their toxic properties, and are a major public hazard. (OPCW, 2024a, b, c)."@en ;
